    "For instance, Chen et al. [19] underscore the importance of integrating synchronized memory modules for multi-robot collaboration.",
    "Communication among agents also plays a significant role, relying heavily on memory to maintain context and interpret messages.",
    "For example, Mandi et al. [104] demonstrate memory-driven communication frameworks that promote a common understanding among agents.",
    "Long-term Memory InteractionThreats.",
    "The storage and retrieval of long-term memory depend heavily on vector databases."
